=======
 EVENT 
=======
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

manage events and who is joining them .. can paste events to topic

| 

  manage events 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *event-add*

    :description: add an event

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-add party bla
        <output> event added


2) *event-adduser*

    :description: add nick to an event

    :permissions: OPER .. EVENT

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-adduser 2 dunk
        <output> can't add dunk to event 2


3) *event-join*

    :description: join an event

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-join 2
        <output> can't add test to event 2


4) *event-list*

    :description: show all events

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-list
        <output> 1) party bla


5) *event-part*

    :description: unsubscribe from an event

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-part 2
        <output> can't remove test from event 2


6) *event-remove*

    :description: delete nick from an event

    :permissions: EVENT .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-remove 3 dunker
        <output> can't remove dunker from event 3


7) *event-topic*

    :description: put events into the topic

    :permissions: EVENT .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-topic
        <output> none
8) *event-who*

    :description: show who joined an event

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-who 2
        <output> can't get data for event 2


9) *event-del*

    :description: delete event

    :permissions: EVENT .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !event-del 2
        <output> can't delete eventnr 2


